rows.label: tev999907_SEL0031
rows.name: This BLADE operative is standing by for orders.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG0101
rows.name: Good day. I'm pleased to see you looking so well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG2001
rows.name:
You'll have nothing to worry about.
We will support you without fail.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG2101
rows.name:
I just hope the support from my division can make
combat a little more pleasant for you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG3001
rows.name: Certainly, if I can be of some service.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG3101
rows.name:
I don't know if I can live up to your expectations,
but I will try.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG5001
rows.name: Forgive me. Can we do this some other time, perhaps?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG5101
rows.name:
I'm honored that you wanted to speak with me,
but I'm afraid I can't talk right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999907_MSG5102
rows.name: Any chance I could get a rain check?[ST:wait ]
